data.description: Cute as a button.  Open and bright home. 3 spacious bedrooms.  Quick access to downtown Colorado Spring and steps away from most major thoroughfares. This home comfortably housed a family of four, and the fenced backyard allowed for room to run, play, and spend time outdoors. This house has all main-level living and convenience for the new buyers. The stainless steel appliances include range/oven, dishwasher, microwave, refrigerator.
